    "body": "### Steps to reproduce the issue\r\n\r\n```console\r\n$ spack install gcc@5.4.0\r\n/tmp/berceanu/spack-stage/spack-stage-h_mzdde2/gcc-5.4.0/spack-build/./gcc/cc1: error while loading shared libraries: libisl.so.13: cannot open shared object file: No such file or directory\r\nchecking for suffix of object files... configure: error: in `/tmp/berceanu/spack-stage/spack-stageh_mzdde2/gcc-5.4.0/spack-build/x86_64-unknown-linux-gnu/libgcc':\r\nconfigure: error: cannot compute suffix of object files: cannot compile\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Platform and user environment\r\n\r\n```commandline\r\n$ uname -a \r\nLinux x470 4.15.0-33-generic #36-Ubuntu SMP Wed Aug 15 16:00:05 UTC 2018 x86_64 x86_64 x86_64 GNU/Linux\r\n$ lsb_release -d\r\nDescription:\tUbuntu 18.04.1 LTS\r\n``` \r\n",
